{"settings":"{
    "files.associations": {
        "*.rsn": "rust"
    },
    "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
    "workbench.colorCustomizations": {
        "editor.lineHighlightBackground": "#1073cf2d",
        "editor.lineHighlightBorder": "#9fced11f"
    },

    "editor.fontFamily": "hack, monospace",
    "editor.fontWeight": "bold",
    "editor.lineHeight": 0,
    "editor.minimap.enabled": false,
    "editor.acceptSuggestionOnEnter": "smart",
    "editor.tabCompletion": "onlySnippets",
    "editor.renderWhitespace": "all",
    "editor.wordWrap": "off",
    "editor.insertSpaces": false,
    "editor.inlayHints.enabled": true,
    "diffEditor.wordWrap": "off",
    "editor.autoClosingQuotes": "always",
    "editor.quickSuggestions": true,
    "editor.suggestOnTriggerCharacters": true,

    "explorer.confirmDragAndDrop": false,
    "explorer.confirmDelete": false,

    "files.trimTrailingWhitespace": true,
    "files.insertFinalNewline": true,
    "files.autoSave": "afterDelay",

    "terminal.integrated.tabs.enabled": true,
    "terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux": "zsh",

    // Git & Gitlens
    "git.autofetch": true,
    "git.confirmSync": false,
    "git.scanRepositories": [
        "~/home/Project"
    ],
    "gitlens.hovers.currentLine.over": "line",
    "gitlens.currentLine.enabled": false,
    "gitlens.views.branches.branches.layout": "list",

    "[markdown]": {
        "editor.wordWrap": "on",
        "editor.quickSuggestions": true
    },

    "projectManager.projectsLocation": "/home/cyril/.config/Code/User/globalStorage/alefragnani.project-manager",
    "projectManager.git.baseFolders": [
        "~/Projects",
        "~/42cursus",
        "~/Rush"
    ],

    // 42 Header & Norminette
	"42norminette.command": "norminette", // Default: 'norminette'.
	"42norminette.showErrors": "all", // Default: 'all'. ['all', 'one']
	"42norminette.trace.server": "off", // Default: 'messages'. ['messages', 'off', 'verbose']
	"42header.username": "cybattis",
	"42header.email": "cybattis@student.42.fr",

    "peacock.favoriteColors": [
        {
            "name": "Angular Red",
            "value": "#dd0531"
        },
        {
            "name": "Azure Blue",
            "value": "#007fff"
        },
        {
            "name": "JavaScript Yellow",
            "value": "#f9e64f"
        },
        {
            "name": "Mandalorian Blue",
            "value": "#1857a4"
        },
        {
            "name": "Node Green",
            "value": "#215732"
        },
        {
            "name": "React Blue",
            "value": "#61dafb"
        },
        {
            "name": "Something Different",
            "value": "#832561"
        },
        {
            "name": "Svelte Orange",
            "value": "#ff3d00"
        },
        {
            "name": "Vue Green",
            "value": "#42b883"
        }
    ],

    "redhat.telemetry.enabled": false,
    "telemetry.telemetryLevel": "off",
    "C_Cpp.updateChannel": "Default",

    "tabnine.experimentalAutoImports": false,

    "cwtools.cache.stellaris": "I:\\SteamLibrary\\steamapps\\common\\Stellaris",

    // Header
    "psi-header.config": {
        "forceToTop": true,
        "blankLinesAfter": 1,
        "copyrightHolder": "<<year>> <<company>>"
    },
    "psi-header.changes-tracking": {
        "isActive": true,
        "modAuthor": "Modified By: ",
        "modDate": "Last Modified: ",
        "modDateFormat": "DD.MM.YYYY, HH:mm:ss",
        "include": [],
        "exclude": [
            "markdown",
            "json"
        ],
        "excludeGlob": [],
        "autoHeader": "manualSave"
    },
    "psi-header.variables": [
        [
            "company",
            "#_#"
        ],
        [
            "author",
            "Stb"
        ],
        [
            "authoremail",
            "contact@cbgr.anonaddy.com"
        ]
    ],
    "psi-header.templates": [
        {
            "language": "*",
            "template": [
                "# File         : <<filename>> #",
                "# Project      : <<projectname>> #",
                "# Author       : <<author>> (<<authoremail>>) #",
                "#---------------------------------------------#",
                "# Created Date : <<filecreated('DD.MM.YYYY, HH:mm:ss')>> #",
                "# Last Modified: #"
            ]
        }
    ],
    "markdown-preview-enhanced.previewTheme": "monokai.css",
    "terminal.integrated.fontFamily": "hack, monospace",
    "workbench.colorTheme": "Gruvbox Dark Medium",
    "workbench.startupEditor": "none",
    "window.zoomLevel": -1,
    "security.workspace.trust.untrustedFiles": "open",
    "workbench.editor.enablePreview": true,
    "editor.foldingHighlight": true,
    "editor.snippetSuggestions": "top",
    "editor.suggest.insertMode": "replace",
    "editor.suggest.preview": false,
    "editor.suggestSelection": "recentlyUsed",
    "editor.rulers": [80]
}
"}
